This map was based on [zm_princeofdarkness](http://www.fpsbanana.com/mips/192 "zm_princeofdarkness")(Zombie Master) by TaiLGaiTeR.
This map at the beginning had to many bug/errors and it took me a few day to turn it to a good aim map, the main error wore Zombie Master textures and props who didn't work in CS:S, air nodes spawn points, unnecessary props and sometimes the map ends in unexpected places where you can't pass throw, but now I think it is good.
Hope you Enjoy.

This map is for free use on any server as long as you agree to:
- Not decompile this map!
- Not claim it as yours
